{"tid":2261253,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立法會戰線手足投錯票 要求支援！！！","createTime":"2020-10-28T07:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T07:54:08.000Z","uid":126889,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"86c6e629c27f58874c7c9d46f928dfc828601058","tid":2261253,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T07:21:18.000Z","msg":"//立法會資深司法任命建議小組委員會周三早上召開會議，討論任命英國最高法院副院長賀知義擔任本港終審法院非常任法官，雖然投票選主席時有7名民主派議員及8名建制派議員在席，但建制派、經民聯梁美芬以9比6擊敗法律界郭榮鏗當選主席主持該次會議，意味一名民主派議員投了票給梁美芬。// <br />\n<br />\n//涂謹申會後查詢時確認有參與投票，但不評論其他議員投票意向。楊岳橋說可能有議員投錯票。郭榮鏗表示，當然投了給自己，但質疑是涂謹申無投票。梁繼昌會後說可能有人投錯票，至於他投票意向，梁繼昌說忘記投了什麼或號碼，「Dennis（郭榮鏗）一號？Priscilla（梁美芬）二號？」//<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/35132/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91-%E8%B3%80%E7%9F%A5%E7%BE%A9%E5%8B%B3%E7%88%B5lord_patrick_hodge-35132/%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%B0%8F%E7%B5%84%E5%AF%A9%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E4%BB%BB%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E4%BB%BB%E5%91%BD-%E9%81%B8%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%80%E7%A5%A8%E9%8C%AF%E6%8A%95%E6%A2%81%E7%BE%8E%E8%8A%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F35132%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583-%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E8%25B3%2580%25E7%259F%25A5%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%258B%25B3%25E7%2588%25B5lord_patrick_hodge-35132%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%2591%25BD-%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B3%259B%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E9%258C%25AF%25E6%258A%2595%25E6%25A2%2581%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%258A%25AC&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7NqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=236df808\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/35132/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83-%E6%B3%9B%E6%B0%91-%E8%B3%80%E7%9F%A5%E7%BE%A9%E5%8B%B3%E7%88%B5lord_patrick_hodge-3